				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok for AEing Dulaks harbour I use a SOW potions ,yes I know we have Selo but tbh its too fast some times heh<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />.
<br />

<br />
Any way once I have SOW going I start with DDD ,yep the AE one you get at lvl 18.
<br />
Then run across the area with the scouts in to the walled area with the two troll guards out side.
<br />
Run in there and aggro all inside.
<br />
Drag them back to the scout area and run round till you have them in a nice bunch,then slowly tighted the circle till you can comfortably get them all in the AE with out them hitting you.
<br />
Most of them seem to drop around the same time,where as the Ore,Steelshapeners and Dock Guardians take longer.
<br />

<br />
What I do is when the majority are down to about 20% health ( by this time the scouts will be dead )I pick a mob ,charm and start it hitting the harder to kill mobs I mentioned above , Snare the target and slow its attack as you dont want it to kill your pet ,, thats lost exp and pp!!.
<br />
Now back to DDDing the rest whilst hitting the targetted one with DDD and Tyuens(SP?) which with epic and selo drum equipped does 104 dmg a tick ( also gets all the other remaining mobs in the AE ).
<br />
On average in an hour I can make in excess of 600 plat due to gems and coin.</span></td>
